  <brief_title>Quality Of Life While Receiving Faslodex</brief_title>
  <official_title>Quality Of Life And Symptoms In Postmenopausal Women With Hormone Receptor Positive Disseminated Breast Cancer While Receiving Faslodex.</official_title>
